text: Þis sent þa landimare to archet þare westere fif hide.
Arest suthward of ealdmannes wyrde at langhecgan to sugging made.

Þane on i richte to stirthel on þane alr beneþen scealden forð & þanen anlang higweges<../images/tbar.gif>of higeweges ande funtemel þry akeres wid eastem þane broc þonne anlang funtmeales oþ eadelmes melne of funtemel to þane twam þornen þat forð on irichte to stigel hege ouer stirtel & þonun on irichte to ginum hocum to þrem land sharen þat on archet hamm.
And þanen cagbroc up anlang cagbroges to land share hegen þonne anlang heges to ealdmannes wyrþe.
